column5: Anyone have any info on Pakwash lake near Ear Falls?
Fished there for 15 years only one week each year about June 1st each year. Good Walleye and northern fishing. Where are you staying?

Fished the Southwest end of the lake last July with good success. Lots of northerns, several walleye and enough smallmouth to make it interesting. Will be at the same place 7/18 to 7/25 this year. I would also like to hear if anyone has a resent report. Thanks, Brad
